title: Amaze Health

creator: Amaze PBC
descriptionHtml:
Take control of your healthcare! Talk live to an Amaze Health doctor from the comfort and convenience of your own home or from wherever you are. Choose a one-time visit or a feature-packed subscription that's right for you. No appointment needed, no waiting room, no insurance required, no contract, and you can cancel a subscription at any time. You can talk live via audio or video, or chat with your medical provider from anywhere using secure messaging.

GETTING STARTED WITH AMAZE HEALTH IS AS SIMPLE AS 1-2-3:
- Download the app
- Create your FREE account
- Choose an affordable one-time visit or one of the monthly subscription options, then Tap on “Talk to a Medical Professional” or “Chat With Us”

Or don’t! Your free account includes all kinds of features to help you take charge of your own healthcare, and we’ll be here when you DO need to talk to a medical professional.

AFFORDABLE OPTIONS THAT WORK FOR YOU
One-time visits include 30 days of follow-up at no additional charge.

Subscription options include a choice of two plans
- Silver Plan: Discounted medical visits and access to premium features like our medical price-shopping tool
- Gold Plan: Unlimited virtual medical care and, in some cases, we can take the place of your primary care provider
- Your choice of billing options for either plan (monthly, quarterly or annual), and either plan can be canceled at any time.

EASY PRESCRIPTION PICKUP AND REFILL
If medically necessary, our providers can write prescriptions and send them to the local pharmacy of your choice.

OUR MEDICAL SERVICES
Our team of medical professionals can treat dozens of common non-emergency medical conditions. If we can’t help you, we’ll help you find a local provider who can.

OTHER AMAZE-ING FEATURES
Keep all your important health insurance and healthcare information in one secure place. Access price-shopping tools for discounts on medications, labs, and imaging; an ad-free healthcare search engine; 1500+ educational medical videos; a best-in-class symptom checker, and more. You can even create your own custom buttons right inside the app.

100% SECURE & CONFIDENTIAL
We take your privacy extremely seriously. Your visits are confidential and HIPAA-compliant. Your data is encrypted and secure.

Amaze is available in most states. Amaze Health does not guarantee patients will receive a prescription, does not prescribe DEA controlled substances, and may not prescribe other drugs which may be harmful due to their potential for abuse.
For complete terms of use, https://amazepbc.com/legal/notices/

creator: Amaze PBC
descriptionHtml:
The Amaze App is a Patient Empowerment Platform.

Amaze is an employer/association sponsored subscription service providing virtual urgent care, virtual primary care, mental health and wellness services, workplace injury triage, and a broad range of education and tools.

Amaze is led by medical providers who help our customers navigate the healthcare system, diagnosing and treating what we can, and providing guidance, referrals and help finding local care when we can’t.

To find out if Amaze is available to you, talk to your employer or association.
